  "comment": "BTF200CZ Fresnel Zoom 200W LED RGBW: BTF200CZ Fresnel Zoom 200W LED RGBW\nThe BTF200CZ Fresnel Zoom is powered with a high power 200W 4-in-1 COB LED to provide superior colour mixing and is designed to replace traditional fresnels. The BTF200CZ is equipped with high-quality optics, a motorized 8-60 degree zoom function and is both dimmable and able to be operated as a strobe up to 19 flashes per second. Ideal for use in theatres, studios, museums, exhibitions or any stage setting that requires smooth warm white output from an energy saving fixture with exceptionally long life. Features Powerconnector in&out and DMX controllability. Supplied with barndoors for beam shaping and glare reduction, safety cord and colour frame.",
